  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You pull back your bow, charging a shot that could even pierce the sky itself. Make a ranged taijutsu attack, dealing your weapon's damage + 5d6.</p><p data-start=\"231\" data-end=\"754\">If this jutsu is used as a Finisher, you instead make a ranged taijutsu attack, dealing your weapon's damage + 8d6, and the target creature must make a Strength saving throw, becoming dazed on a failed save. If a creature would be reduced to 0 as a result of this jutsu, the arrow pierces through their body and continues to travel for an additional 30 feet. If this would collide with another creature's space, you make the attack roll again, taking the damage of this jutsu as if it was not cast as a Finisher on a hit.</p><p data-start=\"756\" data-end=\"979\">At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 2d6. If this jutsu is cast at A-Rank, a creature makes their saving throw with a -2 penalty.</p>",
